obiee.audit.webcat.core

Class WebCatalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • obiee.audit.webcat.core.WebCatalog

  • public class WebCatalog
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an OBIEE Presentation Catalogue or webcat for short. A webcat is a filesystem-based, multi-layered directory structure that serves as the repository for dashboards and reports. Authorisation aspects of an OBIEE implementation such as the roles or users granted access to features or dashboards are also stored within the webcat.
    Author:
    danielgalassi@gmail.com
